{"id":77429,"type":6,"name":"ASSAULT GIRLS","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/85/98/77429_qgqHp.jpg","rating":{"total":4,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":0,"4":0,"5":0,"6":3,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5},"summary":"突击少女(Assault Girls)是由日本导演押井守所拍摄的真人电影。\r\n故事架构在与押井守2001年作品阿瓦隆极度相似的时空背景之下。身着各式武装配备的三女一男，对抗出现在虚拟世界里的变种沙鲸(sandwhales)，这个虚拟世界是能够重现任何场景的虚拟实境游戏 - Avalon。\r\n\r\n延续前作阿瓦隆设定中的虚拟实境游戏Avalon的设定，游戏创作者九姊妹(Nine Sisters)再次加入了实验性的设定Avalon(f)。\r\n在影片开始时四位主角在A级任务中个别对抗终端目标，欲独自获取积分通过A级，但都未成功。因此游戏管理者都建议四人组队，协力击倒终端目标。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>突击少女</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/1287\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">押井守</a></li><li><span>编剧: </span><a href=\"/person/1287\">押井守</a></li><li><span>音乐: </span><a href=\"/person/67\">川井憲次</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/17190\">菊地凛子</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>突击女孩</li><li><span>开始: </span>2009年12月19日</li><li><span>片长: </span>70分</li>","collection":{"wish":7,"collect":6,"doing":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"押井守","count":3},{"name":"电影","count":2},{"name":"菊地凛子","count":2},{"name":"日影","count":2},{"name":"日本","count":1},{"name":"Avalon","count":1},{"name":"ASSAULT_GIRLS","count":1},{"name":"剧场版","count":1},{"name":"川井憲次","count":1},{"name":"2009","count":1},{"name":"特摄","count":1},{"name":"科幻","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":1287,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/85/a5/1287_prsn_Uyo0O.jpg","name":"押井守","desc":"导演"},{"id":67,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/cd/26/67_prsn_3lb13.jpg","name":"川井宪次","desc":"音乐"},{"id":17190,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/da/57/17190_prsn_6Zjzj.jpg","name":"菊地凛子","desc":"主演"}],"relations":[{"id":24160,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/d6/1b/24160_YccH3.jpg","title":"Avalon","type":"前传","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/24160"},{"id":77431,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a8/0f/77431_0cGZI.jpg","title":"斬〜KILL〜","type":"续集","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/77431"},{"id":186513,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ab/ee/186513_5m5kv.jpg","title":"Sand Whale and Me","type":"相同世界观","url":"https://